      "raw_text": "After reading the Straus report the Monroe st..\nbridge this morning the board of public works ordered the\nWashington Water Power Co. to street traffic\never the bridge beginning tomorrow morning Superin\ntenden Huntingdon who attended the meeting said he\nagreed with the board according to the report the\nbridge was liable to collapse at any moment\n\n\nThe orders practically that the bridge will be\nclosed to street until the council either has\nbridge in place the old rebuilt The board also\ndered that all heavy traffic of whatever kind be prohibited\nWaterman will be stationed the bridge to keep off\nheavy loads"
    }
